{"tid":2343831,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"ATM洗倉｜阿里埋單插近8% 兩個月市值蒸發兩萬億 騰訊美團齊挫逾半成","createTime":"2020-12-28T08:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T08:56:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a333439e3286a69fd47e5a3ccbe3f55e47c7537","tid":2343831,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"近期阿里巴巴（9988）可謂禍不單行，先有螞蟻金服未能成功上市，再被市監局立案調查，股份跌完再跌，由超過300元跌至直迫200元，有見及此，公司加大回購力度，阿里公佈，增加股份回購計劃總額，由60億美元增至100億美元，有效期為兩年，並於本季開始執行。公司股價於開市仍要跌逾3%，午後跌幅進一步擴大，並失守210元關，最低見207.2元，見2019年12月31日收市價，最終收市守住210元，跌7.97%，成交達到222.9億元。公司股價今年升幅幾乎全部蒸發。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201228/Z52DZWVIRZED5GLUXP7MB3ZXHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201228%2FZ52DZWVIRZED5GLUXP7MB3ZXHY%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=d5b99b1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201228%2FZ52DZWVIRZED5GLUXP7MB3ZXHY%2F&h=64b84690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201228/Z52DZWVIRZED5GLUXP7MB3ZXHY/</a>"},{"pid":"321d39acd74624010f3eb0225c4966ba96dd2880","tid":2343831,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"犧牲咁大 都要搞馬雲<br />\n落呢個決定嘅人 應該第1個"},{"pid":"6812933fd12ad0e901fcd9ce1281395302aab68b","tid":2343831,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"馬已經服"},{"pid":"a5c9764fc11cff4f5f02963962ed010857c9fed6","tid":2343831,"uid":2054,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0NwLRR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0NwLRR.png&h=1df3344c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"532c2db584025f82511bbea0a7b7e833ec5f8c1e","tid":2343831,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321d39acd74624010f3eb0225c4966b